nodes.text: AT-TE Tank Gunners were elite clone troopers and received ARC training. They operated AT-TE walkers and other armored vehicles.
They wore a black shoulder pauldroun and gray helmet pads, and could step into any role in a transport crew, including piloting and gunnery.[source?]

These troopers were some of the millions of clones of Mandalorian bounty hunter Jango Fett, cloned on Kamino. During the Clone Wars, AT-TE gunners fought on worlds such as Malastare and Ryloth.[source?]
